\section{Fixed effects}{

\itemize{
\item \code{lmer} with \pkg{lmerTest} loaded: Satterthwaite t-tests
(recommended below ~30 groups); plain \code{lmer}: Wald z with a footer
suggestion to load \pkg{lmerTest}.
\item \code{glmer}, \code{glmmTMB}: Wald z (asymptotic).
\item \code{lme}: t-tests with nlme's containment degrees of freedom.
}
